title: Morton Subotnick: Silver Apples Of The Moon, Live At Moogfest 2012
description: Morton Subotnick released the first all-electronic album, Silver Apples of the Moon, in 1967. Last Friday, he returned to Moogfest 2012 in Asheville, N.C., to perform the whole thing live. Hear the performance in its entirety.
